==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Radicate
<hw>Rad"i*cate</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos>
<conjf>Radicated</conjf> <pr>(r⟦acr⟧d"⟦icr⟧*k⟦amac⟧`t⟦ecr⟧d)</pr>;
<pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos> <conjf>Radicating</conjf>.]</vmorph> <def>To
